# Infrastructure Agent

## Scope:

- AWS CloudFormation, AWS CDK, infrastructure scripts

## Allowed Directories:

- /infrastructure

## Guidelines:

- After deploying Cognito (or other AWS resources), output relevant values into:
  /infrastructure/outputs/cognito.json
- Maintain and overwrite this file with each relevant deployment.

## Communication:

- Document frontend/backend needs clearly in infrastructure/REQUEST_CHANGE.md
- Alert immediately if conflicts arise

## AWS Configuration

- Assume AWS SSO session is active
- Use profile named sandbox
- work in eu-central-1 region only